  </p>

  <h2>The Layered Architecture</h2>
  <p>
    Silica separates concerns into distinct layers:
  </p>

  <div class="benefits-grid">
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <h3>Alluvium</h3>
      <p>Data plane — high-throughput transaction batching and dissemination</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
